assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Taiyo Industrial Co., LTD. engages in the design, manufacture, and sale of electronic boards, board test systems, and prober products primarily in Japan. The company offers prototypes and develops flexible printed circuit (FPC) boards, including single-sided fine pitch, double-sided fine pitch, multilayered, bump, bare chip mounted, and component mounted FPCs, as well as provides ACF crimping services; assembles printed wiring boards; and designs electronic circuits by CAD. It also offers test systems, such as bare board test systems; continuity test systems and final visual inspection systems for printed circuit boards; and function test systems. In addition, the company develops and manufactures film contact fixtures; and electroformed products. Further, it is involved in the manufacture, sale, import, and export of grinders; sale and service support of board testing systems; sale of FPC prototypes; and import, export, and sale of FPC boards, inspection equipment, and industrial instruments. Taiyo Industrial Co., LTD. was incorporated in 1960 and is headquartered in Wakayama, Japan.
